data.description: *** Offer Deadline Sun 4/14. Decision to be made Monday, early evening*** Cheerful 3 bedroom home! Updated bath and Kitchen - including granite counters, updated white cabinetry, beautiful backsplash & tiled floor, and stainless steel appliances included! Hardwood Floors throughout much of the first floor. Bonus space upstairs for a possible 4th bedroom and 2 additional bonus spaces in the basement for office/playroom/living space/storage. Separate laundry room with lots of room for storage and a previous owner waterproofed the basement for more peace of mind! Close to shopping, restaurants, and freeways! Seller to provide the C of O for the buyer at closing. Schedule your showing today and be in your new home before summer!!
